	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To the level 20 that is starting epic: Don't.<BR>
The first part of the epic involves giving a SMR to a gnome for a mechanical pen. Keep the SMR if you have it, and wear it until you do the quest at level 50 or beyond. You can't do the quest until then, anyway. You can, however, start gathering some of the components that you will need, like the key on the ledge in OT. I don't know if you can get the snow blossoms you'll need before you start the quest, but give that a shot, too. As for everything else, until you are high enough level to do this particular quest, just get the little components that you can.<BR>
<BR>
If you have any other questions, don't hesitate to ask. Asking is how you learn the easy way.<BR>
<BR>
Zodeeak, 41 Enchanter, Lanys T'Vyl server.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
